Help Type: command
Command: wikigraph <archive-uri>/chapter list

chapter list

Purpose:
  List every chapter in the `.sdpub` chapter tree.

Usage:
  wikigraph <archive-uri>/chapter list [--json] [--llm <json>] [--help|-h]

Output shape:
  [<chapterId>] <stage> <title-or-[untitled]>
  With `--json`, prints `{ "chapters": [...] }`.

Behavior:
  - Includes summary-stage and unfinished chapters.
  - Indents child chapters under their parent.
  - The bracketed number is the chapter id used in chapter URIs.
  - Does not call an LLM provider.
  - Does not mutate chapter content or summaries.

Use this before mutation:
  Discover ids with:
    wikigraph <archive-uri>/chapter list

See also:
  - wikigraph wkg://book.sdpub/state get --help
  - wikigraph wkg://book.sdpub/chapter/3/state get --help
  - wikigraph help command
